ivardefs.name: code
ivardefs.desc: This code defines the purpose of the list - why it was created.

ivardefs.name: date
ivardefs.desc: The date that the list was prepared.

ivardefs.name: emptyReason
ivardefs.desc: If the list is empty, why the list is empty.

ivardefs.name: encounter
ivardefs.desc: The encounter that is the context in which this list was created.

ivardefs.name: identifier_
ivardefs.desc: Identifier for the List assigned for business purposes outside the context of FHIR.

ivardefs.name: mode
ivardefs.desc: How this list was prepared - whether it is a working list that is suitable for being maintained on an ongoing basis, or if it represents a snapshot of a list of items from another source, or whether it is a prepared list where items may be marked as added

ivardefs.name: note_
ivardefs.desc: Comments that apply to the overall list.

ivardefs.name: orderedBy
ivardefs.desc: What order applies to the items in the list.

ivardefs.name: source
ivardefs.desc: The entity responsible for deciding what the contents of the list were. Where the list was created by a human, this is the same as the author of the list.

ivardefs.name: status
ivardefs.desc: Indicates the current state of this list.

ivardefs.name: subject
ivardefs.desc: The common subject (or patient) of the resources that are in the list, if there is one.

ivardefs.name: title
ivardefs.desc: A label for the list assigned by the author.
